high_descs: Walk forwards and then face left towards the kitchen counter
Pick up a cup off of the draining board
Move to your right and face the coffee maker
Set the cup down on the counter to the right of the coffee maker
Turn back to your left
Pick up a fork off of the draining board
Turn back to facing the coffee maker
Put the fork inside the cup
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork on it on the kitchen counter

high_descs: move forward towards the sink
pick up the mug by the side of the sink
turn right towards the coffee maker
drop the mug at the front of the coffee maker
turn left towards the sink
pick up the fork from the sink
turn right towards the coffee maker
place the fork inside the mug
anns.task_desc: place a fork inside the mug on the pavement

high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up a cup from the sink.
Move to the coffee maker to the right of you.
Place the cup on the counter.
Turn and move to the sink to the left of you.
Pick up a fork from the sink.
Move to the coffee maker to the right of you.
Place the fork in the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup near the coffee maker with a fork in it.

high_descs: Walk to the dishwasher, turn to the sink.
Pick up the black cup sitting next to the faucet.
Turn to the coffee pot above the dishwasher.
Sit the cup on the corner of the counter by the coffee pot.
Turn to the left of the sink.
Pick up the fork by the sink.
Turn to the coffee pot.
Put the fork in the black cup.
anns.task_desc: Put the fork in the cup by the coffee pot.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the drinking glass on the counter top that is behind the egg.
Turn to the right to face the other side of the counter.
Place the cup on the counter top in front of the blue coffee maker.
Turn back towards the sink.
Pick up the fork to the right of the potato.
Turn to the right to face the other side of the counter.
Place the fork inside the drinking glass.
anns.task_desc: Move the glass to the other side of the counter top, place the fork inside the cup.
